In a test, there are N problems, each carrying X marks. In each problem, Chef either received X marks or 0 marks.
Determine whether is it possible for Chef to achieve exactly Y marks.






#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
	int N,X,Y;
	scanf("%d%d%d",&N,&X,&Y);
	if(Y%X==0) {
	    printf("YES");
	} else {
	    printf("NO");
	}

}
